---
title: PIP — Pallet ID Pull Flow
---
flowchart TD
    START([Worker opens PIP\nsrc/pages/PIPPage.tsx]) --> S1

    S1[State: selectFunction\nshow CA / CF / FP buttons]
    S1 --> SEL[Worker taps pull function\nhandleSelectFunction]
    SEL --> S2

    S2[State: ready\nlabelField auto-focuses\nvia useEffect on screenState]

    S2 --> SCAN_L{Scanner fires\nor numpad submit\nhandleLabelScan}

    SCAN_L --> API_L[GET /api/labels/:id\napi/functions/labels.ts — getLabel\nvalidate status\nresolve Label→Pallet→Location]

    API_L --> L_FOUND{Found?}
    L_FOUND -->|NOT_FOUND| ERR_L1[Error: Label not found\nlabelField cleared\nremain in ready]
    L_FOUND -->|BAD STATUS\ne.g. PULLED/CANCELLED| ERR_L2[Error: Invalid status\nlabelField cleared\nremain in ready]
    L_FOUND -->|OK| FN_CHECK{pullFunction\nmatch?}

    FN_CHECK -->|Mismatch| ERR_L3[Error: Wrong function\nlabelField cleared\nremain in ready]
    FN_CHECK -->|Match| S3

    ERR_L1 --> S2
    ERR_L2 --> S2
    ERR_L3 --> S2

    S3[State: verifying\nstores labelData\npidField auto-focuses\nvia useEffect on screenState]

    S3 --> RESCAN{New label\nscanned while verifying?}
    RESCAN -->|Yes — handleLabelScan\nissue #45: no status-bar\nupdate on a plain rescan| RELOAD[Clear PID + Alt fields\nreload label data\nsilently]
    RELOAD --> S3

    S3 --> VER_PATH{Worker scans one of:}

    VER_PATH -->|Pallet ID\nPID field| PID_VERIFY[POST /api/pulls/verify\nwith palletId\napi/functions/pulls.ts — verifyPull]
    VER_PATH -->|Alternate ID\nAlt ID field| ALT_VERIFY[POST /api/pulls/verify\nwith alternateId\napi/functions/pulls.ts — verifyPull]

    PID_VERIFY --> PID_OK{Result?}
    PID_OK -->|PALLET_MISMATCH| ERR_PID[Error: Incorrect Pallet ID\npidField cleared + re-focused]
    PID_OK -->|WRONG_PULL_FUNCTION| ERR_PID2[Error: Pull function mismatch]
    PID_OK -->|OK| SUCCESS

    ALT_VERIFY --> ALT_UPC{UPC match?}
    ALT_UPC -->|Yes| ALT_OK
    ALT_UPC -->|No| ALT_BIN{aisle+bin match?}
    ALT_BIN -->|No| ALT_OK
    ALT_BIN -->|Yes| ALT_FN{pullFunction?}
    ALT_FN -->|CA/CF\nlevel ignored| ALT_OK
    ALT_FN -->|FP| ALT_LEVEL{level also\nmatches?}
    ALT_LEVEL -->|Yes| ALT_OK
    ALT_LEVEL -->|No — issues #48/#49\nLEVEL_MISMATCH 400| CONFIRM[ConfirmDialog:\nLevel doesn't match\nYou scanned Level X /\nactual is Level Y]
    CONFIRM -->|Cancel — cancelLevelMismatch| ERR_ALT
    CONFIRM -->|Confirm Pull —\nresubmit with\nconfirmLevelMismatch: true| ALT_OK

    ALT_OK{Result?}
    ALT_OK -->|ALTERNATE_MISMATCH| ERR_ALT[Error: Invalid Alternate ID\naltField cleared + re-focused]
    ALT_OK -->|WRONG_PULL_FUNCTION| ERR_ALT2[Error: Pull function mismatch]
    ALT_OK -->|OK| SUCCESS

    ERR_PID --> S3
    ERR_PID2 --> S3
    ERR_ALT --> S3
    ERR_ALT2 --> S3

    SUCCESS[onPullSuccess\nlabel marked PULLED\nquantities deducted\nwriteLog PUT_PULL]

    SUCCESS --> HIST[Append history entry\nlocation + updatedQty + timestamp]
    HIST --> MSG[MessageBar: success\nPull location + remaining qty]
    MSG --> RESET[Clear all fields\nsetLabelData null\nsetScreenState ready]
    RESET --> S2

    style START fill:#1a1a1a,stroke:#555,color:#fff
    style SUCCESS fill:#003300,stroke:#006600,color:#fff
    style ERR_L1 fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_L2 fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_L3 fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_PID fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_PID2 fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_ALT fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_ALT2 fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style CONFIRM fill:#332200,stroke:#665500,color:#ffcc66
